Mandala m = Create Mandala

Foreach i = 10.0 To 20.0: 

 Number x = i * 10.0

 Shape s = Create Shape:
   Geo triangle 
   Size x
   Color red 
   Rotation 0.0

 Number y = i * 5.0

 Layer l = Create Layer:
   Radius y 
   Shape s 
   Count 8 
   Offset 0.0 
   AngularShift 1

 addTo: (m, l)

draw: (m)